Module com.example.samplesalad
Package com.example.samplesalad.model

Class Pattern

java.lang.Object
com.example.samplesalad.model.Pattern
public class Pattern extends Object
Stores a collection of pad events, representing a musical pattern that can be looped or played in sequence, with each event occurring at specific timestamps.
